  "texts": [
    "Our experiment and results are shown in Section 4.",
    "In section 5, we conclude our approach and further discuss the strength and weakness of our methods.",
    "Problem Definition Image CaptioningThe goal of image captioning is to generate relevant description for given images.",
    "The problem can be thought two-fold as it connects computer vision and natural language processing: 1) use an encoder architecture (CNN, Transformer) [32] to process the image; 2) use a decoder to decode the encoded image representation into sentences.",
    "[16] The model is trained in a supervised learning pattern [11] with some existing image to caption (ground truth) pairs."
  ]
}